{"tid":2140730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"颱風「哈格比」吹襲浙江！女子連人帶窗吹飛直墮 11 樓亡","createTime":"2020-08-05T07:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T11:17:56.000Z","uid":44569,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8560d62ccd60b17bbcb708e2e5b0c753ba56304a","tid":2140730,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2715000/2715564/feng00_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2715000%2F2715564%2Ffeng00_1024.jpg&h=eb631d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據中國媒體報導，「哈格比」是今年第二個登陸內地沿海城市的颱風。浙江溫州、台州等地都狂風暴雨，多條街道被淹沒，當地供電、交通亦受影響。期間，一名居住在玉環市小區的住戶在家中關窗時露台玻璃碎裂，外窗被風吹落，結果連人帶窗掉落 11 層，當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n當局預計，哈格比將持續向偏北方向移動並逐漸減弱。現時，哈格比已造成 500 多間房屋損毀，5,300 多公頃農作物受災，38 萬人受影響。"},{"pid":"cdca2d371c3072801d078859791db29f5d8db002","tid":2140730,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"強國樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f459bbddf8c013650f90504633d2e699c7db84b","tid":2140730,"uid":37680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"成塊窗黎 冇石屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931a970ab8b313176fa81ebac1067f72f75c4502","tid":2140730,"uid":137672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qUjtLpH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqUjtLpH.png&h=4925322c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f20832eeeb102eb49e5458837cac3764608e6610","tid":2140730,"uid":83609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"r